      {"speaker": "安娜", "chinese": "我有一个最佳方案,又省时间又省���。", "pinyin": "Wǒ yǒu yìge zuijia fāng'àn, yòu shěng shíjiān yòu shěng qián.", "english": "I have a perfect solution that saves both time and money."},
      {"speaker": "朴英花", "chinese": "哦? 说说看。", "pinyin": "Ó? Shuōshuō kàn.", "english": "Oh? Tell me."},
      {"speaker": "安娜", "chinese": "周五晚上动身,坐火车卧铺,周六上午到青岛。", "pinyin": "Zhōu wǔ wǎnshang dòngshân, zuò huǒchē wòpù, zhōu liù shàngwǔ dào qīngdào.", "english": "Leave Friday evening, take the train berth, arrive in Qingdao Saturday morning."},
      {"speaker": "安娜", "chinese": "在那儿玩儿一天,当晚再坐长途汽车去曲阜。", "pinyin": "Zài nàr wányǐ tiān, dàngwăn zài zuò chángtú qìchē qù qūfu.", "english": "Play there for a day, then take a long-distance bus to Qufu that night."},
      {"speaker": "朴英花", "chinese": "哇,太棒了!", "pinyin": "Wa, tài bàngle!", "english": "Wow, that's great!"},
      {"speaker": "安娜", "chinese": "别着急,我们在曲阜只玩儿一个白天,然后坐当晚的火车回北京。", "pinyin": "Bié zháojí, wǒmen zài qūfu zhǐ wányǐ ge báitiān, ránhòu zuò dàngwăn de huǒchē huí běijīng.", "english": "Don't worry, we'll spend only one day in Qufu, then take the train back to Beijing that night."}
    ]
